SECTION 1. The following barrios are hereby created in the Municipality of Laoang, Province of Samar:

Barrio of Bonglew, consisting of the sitios of Marubaybay, Beseig, Cagsiburan and Calo-ocan;

Barrio of Cabagoan, consisting of the sitios of Bonot, Matames, Cabagoan and Cangcaligong;

Barrio of Tarosan, consisting of the sitios of Kiki-rohan and Campondong;

Barrio of Inamlan, consisting-of the sitio of Capas-gapas;

Barrio of Bobolusan, consisting of the sitios of Guencalerohan, Doñgon, Dampega, Bon-ot, Herosalem and Guenlambekihan;

Barrio of Cancahepus, consisting of the sitios of Caco-olan, Taboc and Babantayan;

Barrio of Rombang, consisting of the sitios of La-nobe, Cagotsan, Cancarajog and Carawag;

Barrio of Vigo, consisting of the sitios of Malobago, Nalibon, Macalanos, Camalig, Benalenan and Nahibang;

Barrio of Yapas, consisting of the sitios of Tinoblan, Libas and Tomindao;

Barrio of San Antonio, consisting of the sitios of Malobago, Lobogon, Larac, De-it, Hangtud, Bartulo and Son-og;

Barrio of Gregorio B. Tan, consisting of the sitios of Galatan and Camparicay;

Barrio of Aroganga, consisting of the sitios of Sase-on, Manaybanay and Balwarte;

Barrio of Aroganga, consisting of the sitios of Sase-on, Manaybanay and Balwarte;

Barrio of Cabagngan, consisting of the sitios of San Vicente and Pinangorayan;

Barrio of Burabod, consisting of the sitios of Vega, Cagnaga, Bagsang and Amambolanon;

Barrio of Agrupacion, consisting of the sitios of Cawilan, Lengawin and Nabioso;

Barrio of Antipolo, consisting of the sitios of Da-o, Camilig and Balocawe;

Barrio of Lawa-an, consisting of the sitio of Tinbao;

Barrio of Canyomanao, consisting of the sitio of Canamocan ;

Barrio of Lanobe, consisting of the sitio of Ta-wiron;

Barrio of Tenoblan, consisting of the sitio of Carawag; and

Barrio of Suba.
